casebody.data:
CLARK v. WARDEN OF MARYLAND PENITENTIARY [App. No. 52,

September Term, 1962.]

Decided January 30, 1963.

Before the full Court.

PER Curiam.

For the reasons given in the lower court’s opinion, as well as upon the authority of Ellinger v. Warden, 224 Md. 648, this application for leave to appeal from denial of post conviction relief is hereby denied.
